   <div class="mainContent">
    <div class="mainText">
     <h2>
      Welcome to Public Affairs
     </h2>
     <h3>
      Departments
      <br/>
     </h3>
     <p class="linkMenu">
      <a href="BigTenNetwork/index.html">
       Big Ten Network
      </a>
      |
      <a href="http://creativeservices.illinois.edu" target="_blank">
       Creative Services
      </a>
      |
      <a href="http://news.illinois.edu" target="_blank">
       News Bureau
      </a>
      |
      <a href="https://videoservices.illinois.edu" target="_blank">
       Video Services
      </a>
      |
      <a href="marketing/web/webtools.html">
       Web Services
      </a>
     </p>
     <h3>
      Resources
     </h3>
     <p class="linkMenu">
      <a href="http://identitystandards.illinois.edu/" target="_blank">
       Illinois Identity Standards
      </a>
      |
      <a href="https://webtools.illinois.edu" target="_blank">
       Webtools
      </a>
      |
      <a href="http://illinois.edu/about/index.html" target="_blank">
       Campus Facts And Rankings
      </a>
      |
      <a href="staff.html" target="_blank">
       Staff Listing
      </a>
     </p>
     <p>
      Public Affairs provides a broad range of services to help you reach your marketing and communications goals, including crisis communications, copywriting and editing, graphic design, media relations, marketing consulting, seminars and training, and Web site development and tools. As the campus-level strategic communications and marketing unit, we also manage the campus Web site, respond to national surveys, and handle Freedom of Information Act requests in addition to a wide array of special projects.
     </p>
     <p>
      Divisions within Public Affairs include the
      <a href="BigTenNetwork/index.html">
       Big Ten Network
      </a>
      , creating high-quality, non-athletic documentaries aired on the Big Ten Network;
      <a href="http://creativeservices.illinois.edu">
       Creative Services
      </a>
      , providing graphic design and project management service;
      <a href="https://videoservices.illinois.edu">
       Video Services
      </a>
      , producing high quality promotional and marketing videos; the
      <a href="http://news.illinois.edu">
       News Bureau
      </a>
      , delivering research and campus-related press content; and
      <a href="marketing/web/webtools.html">
       Web Services
      </a>
      , offering no-cost Web solutions to campus.
     </p>
     <p>
      Explore this site and discover how Public Affairs can help you tell your story.
     </p>
    </div>
